July 26, 2017 12:47 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of BMC Fund, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
BMC Fund, Inc. is a closed-ended balanced mutual fund launched and managed by Broyhill Investments Inc. The fund invests in the public equity and fixed income markets of the United States. BMC Fund, Inc. was formed in 1982 and is domiciled in the United States.


800 Golfview Park, Po Box 500Lenoir, NC 28645United StatesFounded in 1982



Phone: 828-758-6100








