BMC Fund, Inc. Key Developments

BMC Fund, Inc., Annual General Meeting, Feb 24, 2017
Jan 27 17
BMC Fund, Inc., Annual General Meeting, Feb 24, 2017, at 14:30 US Eastern Standard Time. Location: executive offices of the Fund 800 Golfview Park Lenoir, NC 28645 United States Agenda: To consider the election of 11 directors to hold office until the next annual meeting of shareholders and until their successors have been elected and qualified; and to transact such other business as may properly come before the meeting.


BMC Fund, Inc., Annual General Meeting, Feb 26, 2016
Jan 29 16
BMC Fund, Inc., Annual General Meeting, Feb 26, 2016, at 14:30 Pacific Standard Time. Location: at the executive offices of the Fund, 800 Golfview Park, Lenoir North Carolina 28645 United States Agenda: To elect 12 directors to hold office until the next annual meeting of shareholders and until their successors have been elected and qualified; to transact such other business as may properly come before the meeting.


