            Business Description
        



BMC Fund is located in Lenoir, North Carolina. This organization primarily operates in the Fund Raising Organizations business / industry within the Business Services sector. This organization has been operating for approximately 10 years. BMC Fund is estimated to generate $75,000 in annual revenues, and employs approximately 1 people at this single location.









